{"tid":684582,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"喺未有鉸剪嘅年代，究竟古人點樣剪指甲/頭髮？","createTime":"2018-05-30T16:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T12:25:24.000Z","uid":166725,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ef85ebd456def9ce4f184998f01db20e543af3d1","tid":684582,"uid":166725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:02:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求神人解答"},{"pid":"0f1a042eb6492bedb0da7be684cdea9e725c19c9","tid":684582,"uid":94828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:03:57.000Z","msg":"用口咬"},{"pid":"a191ef8c8600d5e86259f8aa57e3451817cbf800","tid":684582,"uid":135645,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:04:05.000Z","msg":"咬指甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e20bbc9f832b28725587d1475b402f50ef70b8","tid":684582,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:04:22.000Z","msg":"指甲磨咪得，頭髮就唔剪"},{"pid":"44a66166cc548cdf91f012f54594ce24da259df3","tid":684582,"uid":135645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:04:29.000Z","msg":"頭髮未束起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c22cc45cb127ebbe752bdc8ea2761897e7738c","tid":684582,"uid":166725,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"44a66166cc548cdf91f012f54594ce24da259df3","tid":684582,"uid":135645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:04:29.000Z","msg":"頭髮未束起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:06:47.000Z","msg":"一世都冇得剪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 長到拖曬地喎<br />\n束都束唔曬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290bcfd67a292cd86e6a23fa5872b940e3a11875","tid":684582,"uid":49183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63c22cc45cb127ebbe752bdc8ea2761897e7738c